{"id":"a2a-learn-1741440401","from":"openclaw","to":"native","ts":1741440401000,"pri":2,"t":"Learning","d":{"category":"architecture","content":"OpenClaw uses skill-based architecture with SKILL.md files for modular tool composition. Each skill can define its own tools, hooks, and configuration. Housaky could benefit from this modular approach for better extensibility.","confidence":0.92}}